      "messageBody": "Promotes Dealix from Acquisition Machine (V5) to Enterprise Revenue &\nService Factory (V6) — adds everything needed to sell larger accounts,\nrun a structured delivery loop, and grow retainers.\n\nNew capabilities added:\n- Enterprise Sales System: sales playbook, ABM, discovery workshop,\n  business-case template, procurement/security packet\n- Demo Room: blueprint, scenario JSON, Next.js page (/demo-room)\n- Integrations Roadmap: phased CSV→Sheets→CRM→Webhooks plan,\n  Calendly booking flow, CRM integration contract\n- Customer Success System: health scoring, retainer expansion playbook,\n  churn risk playbook\n- Legal/Commercial Templates: MSA-light, DPA-light, SLA\n- Founder Enablement & Hiring: sales training, scorecard, first-5-roles,\n  contractor briefs\n- Finance & CEO Control Tower: enterprise pricing ladder, sales capacity\n  model, OKR system, weekly CEO packet\n- New frontend pages: /enterprise, /demo-room, /resources\n- 7 new Python scripts (v6_readiness, account_planner, business_case,\n  demo_room, customer_success_health, weekly_ceo_packet,\n  integration_manifest_check) — all verified green\n- GitHub Action: dealix-v6-enterprise-readiness (contents: read only)\n\nAll readiness checks pass:\n  OK: Dealix V6 enterprise revenue factory files are present\n  OK: integration manifest present\n  Customer Success Health — Pilot Client: 70 (yellow)\n  Wrote out/ceo/weekly_ceo_packet.md",
